Package: Kdirectional
Type: Package
Title: Analysis of anisotropy in point patterns using second order statistics
Version: 1.0
Date: 2015-06-06
Author: Tuomas Rajala
Maintainer: Tuomas Rajala <tuomas.rajala@iki.fi>
Description: Tools for analysing linear transformations of 2D and 3D point
    patterns. Includes directed summary statistics, and scaling+rotation estimations
    using Fry points.
License: GPL
Depends:
    Rcpp (>= 0.10.6),
    sphere,
    ellipsoid
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Suggests:
    knitr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
